      "text": "3D Global Position: [x,y,z]\n3D Global Velocity: [vx, vy, vz]\n4D Orientation (Attitude): Represented as a quaternion [qw, qx, qy, qz]\nIMU Sensor Biases: accelerometer [bx, by, bz] and gyroscope [bp, bq, br]\n\ntrack 6 dofs --> translational & rotational ​\n",
